== Anadi ussnan == 
Tamhazt n [[anadi ussnan|unadi ussnan]] deg tasdawit n Bgayet tella deg usfari ameɣlal, tettwegenses tura sɣur 20 [[Inegmi n unadi|inegmiyen n unadi]], yetwanesgerzen sɣur Uɣlif n Usselmed imineg d Unadi Ussnan. Asselhu n [[tafarest tussnant]] (am ɣef uɣawas n tasmekta am ɣef uɣawas n taɣara) d yiwen n iswan igejdanen i tebɣa ad ttawey tasdawit deg ukatar n ussisen ines i tallalt n unadi ussnan. Tafarest tussnant n tasdawit n Bgayet tetwesbuɣer deg useggwas [[2008]] s 76 [[tasufiɣt tussnant|tisufaɣ]] tigraɣlanin d 231 tiɣwalin tigraɣlanin.

Umuɣ n Inegmiyen n unadi n tasdawit n Bgayet :

*Inegmi n taknussna n tinegwa dɣa n tasmedna n tisetwal
*Inegmi n tinegwa tigemnawin
*Inegmi n tasmedna dɣa n tawennaḍt
*Inegmi n timeswi dɣa n tawennaḍt
*Inegmi n tasmedna n trisiti
*Inegmi n taseɣreft d usekkey n inagrawen (LAMOS)
*Inegmi n tasengama taẓrayant (LPT)
*Inegmi tasnudermẓit yettwasensen
*Inegmi n azduɣwal d tawennaḍt
*Inegmi n tuder-tusnakt, tudertasengama tudertakrura
*Inegmi n unadi deg inagrawen azduγwalanen dɣa awlal d amankriz
*Inegmi azduɣwal n imẓudren
*Inegmi tudertaknussna timɣawiyin d titniethno-taḥcict
*Inegmi n tadamsa d taneflit
*Inegmi n ussileɣ deg tutlayin yettwasensen d tijjenyeṛt n tutlayin deg tawennaḍt agetutlayt
*Inegmi n tasmedna n lbenyan d tasegda
*Inegmi Agertugrint Tadawsa d Amezdaɣ

==Amyalel agraɣlan==
Tasdawit n Bgayet tella deg timezziraz namyalel ussnan agraɣlan ameqran. Deg axleq ines, tasdawit tezmel imtawayen n imyallen ager-isdawanen am s tisdawiyin tiṛumiyin, tispenyuliyin, tikanadiyin d timarikaniyin<ref>http://www.latribune-online.com/suplements/thema/73751.html</ref>. Tasdawit n Bgayet d amaslaḍ n aṭas iẓeḍwan igraɣlanen isdawanen : Averoès [[Erasmus mundus]]<ref>http://www.elwatan.com/regions/kabylie/bajaia/bejaia-l-universite-prepare-la-prochaine-rentree-23-07-2013-222045_143.php</ref>, TEMPUS, CMEP, DEF/CNRS, PCIM.

